 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;1 1 []&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:14px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mk1cubpi1ckh\">如果你是 Claude Code、Vs Code 的重度用户，可以研究研究。</span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;1 1 []&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:14px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mk1cubpi246m\">目前已经在 GitHub 上获得 2000 的 Star 了。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:16px;margin-right:8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"100046700\" data-ratio=\"0.5546296296296296\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=8031e16e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FePw3ZeGRruzlgHDbnhTC0spOibBmkJDoGfn6ZH9QeHCBCFTJsNIibnhXRcZIxJuLibE3lSbqAdbItSwxpJd3iaKeDw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p class=\"js_darkmode__0\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:32px 8px 0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);font-family: Futura-Medium;font-size: 32px;font-weight: 700;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">01</span></span></p>\n  <p class=\"js_darkmode__1\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 16px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><strong class=\"js_darkmode__2\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;padding:0px;margin:0px;outline:0px;max-width:100%;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 16px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">开源项目简介</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" mpa-font-style=\"mk1cubpi1r0p\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">使用这个开源项目，你可以通过「拖拽节点」的方式，<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">像画流程图一样来设计 Claude Code 的自动化任务、技能（Skills）和复杂的 Agent 逻辑</span>，而不需要纯靠手写复杂的代码或配置文件。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:14px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mk1cubpib8w\">除了部分你需要联网的 MCP 工具外，这个插件的所有编辑和生成逻辑都是在你的 VS Code 本地运行的，<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">不会把你的隐私配置乱传到云端。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:14px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mk1cubpi1p69\">而且界面会根据你的 VS Code 语言设置自动切换，支持中文。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:16px;margin-right:8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"100046701\" data-ratio=\"0.6240740740740741\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b3592af5&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FePw3ZeGRruzlgHDbnhTC0spOibBmkJDoGMuONgBC4ZkLiaY07kEbbLXlvstEVXazroZez0qmNSLS0XcRAib9arEuw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><ms-cmark-node><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:14px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mk1cubpi1uo1\">这个插件左边有各种节点，比如提示词、子智能体、人工确认、条件判断等。</span></ms-cmark-node></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><ms-cmark-node><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:14px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mk1cubpi1hfv\">你可以通过可视化拖拽的方式，搭建出来一个自动化流程。</span></ms-cmark-node></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><ms-cmark-node><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mk1cvjl5145d\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mk1cvjlc23op\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 122, 170);font-weight: bold;\">AI 对话生成工作流</span></span></ms-cmark-node></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"2 2 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:14px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, sy